<br>
What I've noticed from personal experience is that there comes a point where you have everything you want. Once you hit that point, money, and assets, just continue to pile up. It's kind of like EQ in that respect: you reach a point where there simply isn't any buyable upgrade to your gear, and once you hit that point, the cash just starts to collect.<br>
